msgctxt "Talk_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I ask you, Furosa, is there anything\n"
"better than a taste of <2.se_co>Noble Pursuit<3.re_co>?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You were at death's door and you ran\n"
"all the way here for that! Good grief... \n"
"You're in incredible shape...\n"
"Does that mean you don't plan to\n"
"investigate that shrine anymore?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Definitely. I never dreamed that kind of\n"
"work would be so dull..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm not surprised you found it dull.\n"
"That sort of thing isn't really \"you.\""
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Yeah, you know what really is \"me\"?\n"
"Drinking."
msgstr ""

